        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/f18816cd4d10b81b8610917baa51d71a_6406089043228945462.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>被动技能</color>\n【被动】战斗开始时，初始附属 <color=#ffffff>诸愿百眼之轮</color> 。"
